    <summary><span data-ttu-id="90b54-101">實作事件提供者，以便使用範本來定義和格式化作為事件通知所傳送的電子郵件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-101">Implements an event provider that uses templates to define and format emails it sends for event notifications.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b54-102">ASP.NET 健康監視，可讓生產環境和作業人員管理已部署的 Web 應用程式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-102">ASP.NET health monitoring allows production and operations staff to manage deployed Web applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b54-103"><xref:System.Web.Management?displayProperty=nameWithType>命名空間包含負責封裝應用程式健全狀況狀態資料，並負責處理此資料提供者類型的健康狀態事件類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-103">The <xref:System.Web.Management?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace contains the health event types responsible for packaging application health-status data and the provider types responsible for processing this data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b54-104">它也會包含有助於管理健全狀況事件的支援型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-104">It also contains supporting types that help during the management of health events.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b54-105">這個類別並不適合從程式碼使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-105">This class is not intended to be used from your code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b54-106">建立、 設定，並由 ASP.NET 狀況監控系統，透過電子郵件傳送事件通知。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-106">It is created, configured, and used by the ASP.NET health-monitoring system to send event notifications by email.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b54-107">本主題的範例 > 一節所示，您可以在組態檔中，定義 Web 事件提供者的電子郵件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-107">You can define an email Web event provider in a configuration file, as demonstrated in the Example section of this topic.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b54-108">此外，您可以設定的提供者區段以程式設計方式存取<xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.Providers%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-108">In addition, you can configure the providers section programmatically by accessing the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.Providers%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b54-109">這個類別會產生電子郵件定義，並使用範本來格式化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-109">The email this class produces is defined and formatted using a template.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b54-110">此範本是由輸出訊息內文的文字的標準的.aspx 檔案中定義的標記程式碼所組成。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-110">This template consists of markup code defined in a standard .aspx file that outputs the text for the message body.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="90b54-111">範本所使用的事件資訊由<xref:System.Web.Management.MailEventNotificationInfo>物件所提供的靜態<xref:System.Web.Management.TemplatedMailWebEventProvider.CurrentNotification%2A>這個類別的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-111">The event information used by the template is provided by a <xref:System.Web.Management.MailEventNotificationInfo> object that is available from the static <xref:System.Web.Management.TemplatedMailWebEventProvider.CurrentNotification%2A> property of this class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b54-112">此提供者會有一組完整的組態屬性，您可以使用來自訂它的運作的方式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-112">This provider has a comprehensive set of configuration attributes that you can use to customize the way it works.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="90b54-113">下列範例會示範如何指定的型別提供者的組態檔案摘錄<xref:System.Web.Management.SimpleMailWebEventProvider>中`<healthMonitoring>` 區段`<add>`中的項目`<rules>`區段中，指定提供者會處理要求處理錯誤和基礎結構錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="90b54-113">The following example is a configuration file excerpt that shows how to specify a provider of type <xref:System.Web.Management.SimpleMailWebEventProvider> in the `<healthMonitoring>` section The `<add>` elements in the `<rules>` section specify that the provider will handle request-processing errors and infrastructure errors.</span></span>  
  
```  
<system.web>  
  <healthMonitoring  
    enabled="true"  
    heartBeatInterval="0">  
    <bufferModes>  
      <add name="Critical Notification"  
        maxBufferSize="100"  
        maxFlushSize="20"  
        urgentFlushThreshold="1"  
        regularFlushInterval="Infinite"  
        urgentFlushInterval="00:01:00"  
        maxBufferThreads="1"  
      />  
    </bufferModes>  
    <providers>  
      <add name="CriticalMailEventProvider"  
        type="System.Web.Management.TemplatedMailWebEventProvider,   
        System.Web, Version=%ASSEMBLY_VERSION%, Culture=neutral,   
        PublicKeyToken=%MICROSOFT_PUBLICKEY%"  
        template="../mailtemplates/critical.aspx"  
        from="sender address"  
        to="someone@example.com"   
        cc="someone@example.com"  
        bcc="someone@example.com"  
        priority="High"  
        bodyHeader="Warning!"  
        bodyFooter="Please investigate ASAP."  
        subjectPrefix="Action required."  
        buffer="true"  
        bufferMode="Critical Notification"  
        maxEventLength="4096"  
        maxSize="4096"  
        maxMessagesPerNotification="1"  
      />  
    </providers>  
    <eventMappings>  
      <add name="Request Processing Events"  
        type="System.Web.Management.WebRequestEvent, System.Web",   
        Version=%ASSEMBLY_VERSION%, Culture=neutral,   
        PublicKeyToken=%MICROSOFT_PUBLICKEY%"   
      />  
      <add name="Infrastructure Errors"  
        type="System.Web.Management.WebErrorEvent, System.Web,   
        Version=%ASSEMBLY_VERSION%, Culture=neutral,   
        PublicKeyToken=%MICROSOFT_PUBLICKEY%"   
      />  
    </eventMappings>  
    <profiles>  
      <add name="Default"  
        minInstances="1"  
        maxLimit="Infinite"  
        minInterval="00:10:00"  
      />  
      <add name="Critical"  
        minInstances="1"  
        maxLimit="1024"  
        minInterval="00:00:00"  
      />  
    </profiles>  
    <rules>  
      <add name="Request Processing Errors"  
        eventName="Request Processing Errors"  
        provider="CriticalMailEventProvider"  
        profile="Default"  
      />  
      <add name="Infrastructure Notifications"  
        eventName="Infrastructure Errors"  
        provider="CriticalMailEventProvider"  
        profile="Critical"  
      />  
    </rules>  
  </healthMonitoring>   
</system.web>  
```  
  
 ]]></format>
